.DT
query_co_ords
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_co_ords

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_co_ords -  This method returns the coordinates for the specified directory.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
mapping query_co_ords(string dir)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^dir%^RESET%^ - the directory to return the coordinates for
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the coordinates mapping
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/map.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the coordinates for the specified directory.
The mapping containers keys of the room and the values are the
coordinates of the room.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
change_co_ords()

.EP

